        <mxCell id="metadata-text" value="Services: globalAIService.js, deviationAnalyzer.js, usageTracker.js | Tables: Deviation, TestRun, TestRunStep, AIProvider | Triggered: Automatically after test failure | Non-Blocking: Test result saved first, analysis runs async | Industry Pattern: Sentry, Datadog Error Tracking | Last Updated: 2025-12-12 | Complexity: Medium (40+ nodes, 5 lanes)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=6.5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
